Package com.googlecode.cqengine.codegen

Class MemberFilters

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.googlecode.cqengine.codegen.MemberFilters
  • public class MemberFilters
extends Object
    Provides some general purpose MemberFilters which can be used with AttributeSourceGenerator or AttributeBytecodeGenerator.

    • Field Summary

      Fields 
      Modifier and Type Field Description
      static MemberFilter ALL_MEMBERS
      A filter which matches all members (both fields and methods).
      static MemberFilter FIELDS_ONLY
      A filter which matches all fields.
      static MemberFilter GETTER_METHODS_ONLY
      A filter which matches all methods which start with "get", "is" and "has" and where the following character is in uppercase.
      static MemberFilter METHODS_ONLY
      A filter which matches all methods.
